'''Mary Henderson''' was the author of [[Star Wars: The Magic of Myth (book)|''Star Wars: The Magic of Myth'']]. She also appeared in interviews for [[Wikipedia:The History Channel|The History Channel's]] documentary ''[[Star Wars: The Legacy Revealed]]''. Henderson serves as curator for the [[Wikipedia:National Air and Space Museum|National Air and Space Museum]] of the [[Wikipedia:Smithsonian Institution|Smithsonian Institution]].<ref>{{SWArchive|url=community/event/museum/news20020104.html|text=''Magic of Myth'' Heading to Brooklyn}}</ref>

